WEBVTT

00:03:59.057 --> 00:04:02.612
I really do believe that I am
entirely ordinary,

00:04:02.636 --> 00:04:06.426
and my story is so representative
of so many other people.

00:04:07.695 --> 00:04:10.611
CA: Well, there are a billion and a half
Muslims in the world,

00:04:10.635 --> 00:04:13.800
and I guess no one who cares
about the world, actually,

00:04:13.824 --> 00:04:17.597
can avoid a conversation about Islam,

00:04:17.621 --> 00:04:20.091
even if they're not Muslim themselves.

00:04:21.100 --> 00:04:25.484
Islam is deeply involved in so many
aspects of world politics.

00:04:25.508 --> 00:04:29.954
So many of the scariest, hardest debates
and conversations about the future

00:04:29.978 --> 00:04:31.300
involve Islam in some way,